{"tid":1572683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］如何自保","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:25:09.000Z","uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6595687866e04fe6d7dd5f84298c00def4c7a1b","tid":1572683,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"如果咁不幸咁遇到黑社會亂打人應點自保？<br />\n自己都係青年人，應該都算高危一族。重要係女仔，應該唔夠啲黑社會大佬大力，點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問都唔太識化妝化老自己，同埋化妝都需時。想問買定套伊斯蘭服裝（全黑，淨係見到對眼嗰啲）旁身有冇用？著定或者有咩事入廁所快快手換咗佢，起碼睇唔到你幾多歲。咁做會唔會相對安全小小？<br />\n<br />\n得閑都會睇下教自衛術嗰啲片。"},{"pid":"f3b405ba0fea758297aa0f932dbff75cc6922bfc","tid":1572683,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"915 - 進步，改善，突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e6fc7c5131489759e69913b4237332cb85394a22","tid":1572683,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}